title: Bottega Veneta The Pouch
description: Bottega Veneta 'The Pouch' shoulder bag in brown calfskin leather. Featuring ruched detailing, and concealed magnetic closure. This opens to a colour matching leather interior. Approximate dimensions: 36cm(Base-L) x 20cm(H) x 15cm(D), handle drop 13cm. Accompanied by BV tag and dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
